{{Infobox Union |name= Fédération syndicale unitaire |country= [[France]] |members= 162,000 |image= [[Image:Logo fsu.PNG]] |founded= 1993 |current= |head= |dissolved_date= |dissolved_state= |merged_into= |office= 104 rue Romain Rolland 93260 [[Les Lilas]] |people= Bernadette Groison (General Secretary) |website= [http://www.fsu.fr/ www.fsu.fr] |footnotes= }}
The '''Fédération syndicale unitaire''' is the main [[trade union]] in the [[education]] sector in [[France]] and the largest trade union in the [[public sector]]. It has 162,000 members, of whom 88% are teachers.
It is organised on the same lines as its predecessor, the [[Fédération de l'éducation nationale]].
The general secretary is Bernadette Groison.
