The '''Intel Foundation Achievement Awards''' are US$5,000 [[scholarship]]s presented to high school students in recognition of their achievements in the [[scientific]] disciplines. Up to 15 are awarded, on selection by a panel of judges, each year at the [[Intel International Science and Engineering Fair]] (ISEF).

